                "invention-title": [
                    "Molten carbonate power generation system with coal bed gas as raw material and power generation method",
                    "一种以煤层气为原料的熔融碳酸盐发电系统及发电方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a molten carbonate power generation system taking coal bed gas as a raw material and a power generation method. The system comprises a methane high-temperature reforming unit (4), a CO conversion unit (6), a CO2 adsorption unit (7) and a molten carbonate fuel cell power generation unit (9), the methane high-temperature reforming unit is used for carrying out methane high-temperature reforming reaction in which methane is in contact with water vapor to generate CO and H2; the CO conversion unit is used for carrying out CO conversion reaction in which CO is in contact with water vapor to generate CO2 and H2; the CO2 adsorption unit comprises a second mixed gas inlet, a CO2 adsorbent and a high-purity hydrogen outlet, the second mixed gas inlet is communicated with the second mixed gas outlet of the CO conversion unit, and the high-purity hydrogen outlet is communicated with the gas inlet of the anode of the molten carbonate fuel cell power generation unit. Efficient resource utilization of the coal bed gas can be achieved, and the greenhouse effect and resource waste caused by direct discharging of the coal bed gas are avoided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本公开涉及一种以煤层气为原料的熔融碳酸盐发电系统及发电方法，该系统包括甲烷高温重整单元(4)、CO变换单元(6)、CO2吸附单元(7)和融碳酸盐燃料电池发电单元(9)；甲烷高温重整单元用于发生甲烷与水蒸气接触生成CO和H2的甲烷高温重整反应；CO变换单元用于发生CO与水蒸气接触生成CO2和H2的CO变换反应；CO2吸附单元包括第二混合气进口、CO2吸附剂和高纯氢气出口，第二混合气进口与CO变换单元的第二混合气出口连通，高纯氢气出口与熔融碳酸盐燃料电池发电单元阳极的进气口连通。本公开可以实现煤层气的高效资源利用，避免直排煤层气造成的温室效应与资源浪费。"
                }
            ]
